Maps:
    Definition:
      - Analogy of a object/collection/dictionary
      - Allow us to define a kind of dictionary to store in a variable
      - Syntax => $mapName:("key1":value, "key2":value2, ...)
                  To call this we use:
                  => map-get($mapName, key)
                     this will return the respective value!!
    
    Get the values:
      - map-get($mapName, "key")
    
    hasKey:
      - map-has-key(mapName, "key") //true or false
    
    remove key:
      - map-remove(mapName, "key")

    merge:
      - map-merge(mapName1, mapName2)
      - map-merge(mapName1, ("key1":value, "key2":value2, ..))

    
    Nest maps:
      - We can nest various maps, this is useful for helper/utilies functions
      

    
